{"sections":{"768c1e62-8002-4176-89c6-e539137ed427":{"type":"featured-content","disabled":true,"settings":{"show_on_desktop":true,"show_on_mobile":true,"title":"About Us","text":"<p><\/p><h3><\/h3><p><strong>Edwin's Tire Shop: Your Trusted Community Partner for 13 Years<\/strong><\/p><p>Welcome to Edwin's Tire Shop, a cornerstone of quality and reliability in our community since 2010. Founded by Edwin, a passionate mechanic with a vision, our shop has been dedicated to providing exceptional tire services for over a decade.<\/p><p><strong>Our Journey:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>13 Years of Excellence:<\/strong> We've grown alongside our community, building relationships and trust one tire at a time.<\/li><li><strong>Customer Trust:<\/strong> Our commitment to honesty and quality service has earned us a loyal customer base.<\/li><li><strong>High Ratings:<\/strong> With over 102 reviews and an impressive 4.4-star average rating, our reputation speaks for itself.<\/li><\/ul><p><\/p><p>Visit us to experience the difference that dedication and expertise bring to your vehicle. At Edwin's Tire Shop, we're not just changing tires; we're driving community connections.<\/p>","section_style":"section-blank","text_size":"large","text_alignment":"","button_style":"btn--primary","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"1f829c10-8663-4dac-8ac2-8755f8781fa4":{"type":"featured-columns","blocks":{"template--15733362524297__1f829c10-8663-4dac-8ac2-8755f8781fa4-text_block-1":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/acima_logo.png","image_link":"","icon":"location_on","heading_text":"Acima Leasing","text":"<p>offers a lease-to-own program where you can pay over time or buy early to save.<\/p>","button_style":"btn--primary","button_label":"Apply Now","button_link":"https:\/\/acima.us\/oySgayRrudUUmvEa"}},"template--15733362524297__1f829c10-8663-4dac-8ac2-8755f8781fa4-text_block-2":{"type":"text_block","settings":{"title":"","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_im